Combine kale, bell peppers, carrots and 3/4 cup peanuts in a large bowl. Place remaining ingredients in Oster(R) Versa(R) Performance Blender; add remaining peanuts. Blend on HIGH for 1-1/2 to 2 minutes or until combined. (Do not grind peanuts completely.) Pour desired amount of dressing over kale mixture and toss to coat. Serve salad immediately or refrigerate, covered, up to 1 day before serving.